{"tid":416222,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"趣blogblog：敢供樓，點解唔敢供股票","createTime":"2017-09-27T15:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T14:27:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad077c3d8a1e9631e389021491d66c23a4214e2","tid":416222,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:17:28.000Z","msg":"「十年一劫，逢七必跌」，對連升8個月的港股而言，跌市魔咒完全失效。散戶對港股的熱情，對比10年前可謂天與地，市民對大市患得患失的心情，又畏高又想分一杯羹，在成交上已反映一切。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n領展回報達168%<br />\n很多網友會詢問某隻股票是否值得長揸，入貨後隔了數天見股價異動，卻急急腳沽貨，口裏說中長線，其實是即日鮮。真正長揸的，恐怕是股價急跌變蟹貨，卻不願止蝕，無奈地坐艇等運到。<br />\n在此專欄一直建議讀者月供股票，除了本身MPF all in恒指基金，亦月供領展（823）以及長江基建（1038），趁有銀行提供首3年零手續費月供股票計劃，亦加碼月供煤氣（003）及港鐵（066）。月供股票的好處，是無懼市況波動及不會估算大市見頂與否，時間越耐，複式效應越大。<br />\n統計過去10年（2007年9月至2017年8月）煤氣股價紀錄，假設月供定額5,000元，合共買到的股票總數是34,846股，但10年間曾9次送紅股（十送一），累計下來，10年間累積到的股票數目是57,400股，較實際買到的多65%。十年間合共斥資了60萬元，而最新持股市值是85.64萬元，連同10年間收取合共8.15萬元股息，回報是33.8萬或56%。<br />\n另一個例子港鐵，以同樣10年期限，同樣月供5,000元，合共買到的股票總數是20,627股，雖則沒有送紅股，但期間股價穩定向上，更可觀是股息收入達到19萬元（曾連續兩年派2.2元特別息）。10年以來，本金60萬元，持股市值是94.88萬元，連同十年間收取股息，回報是54萬或90%。而領展及長建，回報更達168%及83%。<br />\n月供股票，最重要是持之以恆，以10年以上為目標，這才能盡享複式效應及食盡整個升跌市周期。當然，選擇月供甚麼股票，回報亦相當參差，大家決定前不妨做定功課，選擇一隻心水股票，然後計算其過去十年總回報及往績，而非單單聽坊間專家意見。<br />\n香港有個怪現象，敢供樓，卻不願供股票。槓桿效應下，樓價過去10年升幅達到兩倍甚至更高，惟月供穩陣公用股股票，除非大家覺得可以不搭地鐵、不用煤氣等，否則沒槓桿的資產投資，有近一倍甚至更高回報，不失為退休以至為兒女教育基金投資工具。<br />\n月供股票，不用理升市或跌市、牛市定熊市，終日炒炒賣賣，營營役役，結果很可能得個桔。<br />\n<br />\n股榮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170910/large/b0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170910%2Flarge%2Fb0203a.gif&h=5241cbe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170910/20148356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170910%2F20148356&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b121fa31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170910%2F20148356&h=028d9ba7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170910/20148356</a>"},{"pid":"109033da174164969fb5a4031e30e60e5d098ef7","tid":416222,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9526ebbaf4ed68940e816aa33c6949acc342a073","tid":416222,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T23:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77b9fe30a7db31628355f4725d2d0052a3f96fe","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:02:31.000Z","msg":"有看此篇。因為D人認為磗頭有渣過拿過股票。但係供股票供幾多可以控制，負擔到喎。開始供樓就要死慳爛慳，仲要找秘撈"},{"pid":"1aed0d4e8f0a923a2f103f5878a9891fbec60f5e","tid":416222,"uid":895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"如果月供了當年既大藍籌利豐 屍變環球 or 遠古d既香港電訊會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a018b184182f354e522108bd15ecf2df78ef00a","tid":416222,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:07:23.000Z","msg":"注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP"},{"pid":"d2ac3c7d81dd4adc44cc7b70caf9733ed568cc4f","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果月供了當年既大藍籌利豐 屍變環球 or 遠古d既香港電訊會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n供股揀長線穩當，有息收為上。D股唔係直線上升架嘛，如果供下供下隻股隻跌，心裡受唔受得住?<br />\n我供隻騰訊#700，仲有一個月供滿啦(不是銀行月供，是買哂哂貨分期供)! 200元左右買入，分12期供，YEAH!"},{"pid":"42b753ae8e776401a0cf3acfd3ffae51b6ae64d0","tid":416222,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果月供了當年既大藍籌利豐 屍變環球 or 遠古d既香港電訊會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n供股揀長線穩當，有息收為上。D股唔係直線上升架嘛，如果供下供下隻股隻跌，心裡受唔受得住?<br />\n我供隻騰訊#700，仲有一個月供滿啦(不是銀行月供，是買哂哂貨分期供)! 200元左右買入，分12期供，YEAH!</blockquote><br />\n邊到有得咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fa73743f6d2639a533bfb878fec7b83ea67721","tid":416222,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"香港啲垃圾供嚟把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283c20d072a371f8a4eabb39427e67de43fdcaeb","tid":416222,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"為左呃稿費可以去到幾盡"},{"pid":"44f02f30519fb109cade07d5bab0d6562ff3c9f6","tid":416222,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP</blockquote><br />\n應該供指數"},{"pid":"4ce3a31d7168c1157ebb49ef50976b1f45ac811a","tid":416222,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP</blockquote><br />\n如果真係買大公司呢？<br />\n港鐵之類？"},{"pid":"2506c3c51f3ebb0af997baf8a5791253567aac3e","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:54:51.000Z","msg":"在香港有2間證券行係可以咁俾客供股票。你可以去比較下息口同彈性。提示：我爸叫(耀輝)。"},{"pid":"6a93e17aab0be214e7a637a65be7920c000df12f","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"如果我早點有錢供港鐵就好了.......有價有息"},{"pid":"e8248205eacbab572408f551ace8fb7158ef6c16","tid":416222,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:57:15.000Z","msg":"點都唔係而家開始供掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2f1e1ea6e40a3bafc0413ce21e7d20b5b585b5","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP</blockquote><br />\n應該供指數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以供ETF,基金之類"},{"pid":"e54278bd2622f030c8e0ac8c94af3c499b0e2d7e","tid":416222,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"開始吹噓就真係離一劫不遠"},{"pid":"d90dbf12757b4846d9011cd2a6011d82034849e1","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"唔係呀，苹果篇文都發人深省。供樓是多少人心里的痛"},{"pid":"c3ccaa9830e62f06fd2e50a61f4a2564f6231296","tid":416222,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP</blockquote><br />\n應該供指數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以供ETF,基金之類</blockquote><br />\n#2800 <br />\n保險，基金之類就免"},{"pid":"4c1bd1d402ee4ea1475489626443e38ad2a83471","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點都唔係而家開始供掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點都要揀隻去儲。我有個同年紀的同事，一出手的投資金額比我大7倍，嗚嗚.....點解我唔早D諗理財的問題?早年淨識買消息股蝕左去。"},{"pid":"b53ffec98a243c339cd7bf16299c457ff9ef9df1","tid":416222,"uid":34976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>注意買入單一/某幾間公司既風險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgreenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html&d=e2%2FxZGPKeIhR2CFKupGpyIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2187391d\" target=\"_blank\">http://greenhornfinancefootnote.blogspot.hk/2017/09/2the-dismal-outcome-of-betting-on-one.html</a><br />\n<br />\n供股唔係萬能, 亦要記住你買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n買中下一間思捷環球只能講聲RIP</blockquote><br />\n如果真係買大公司呢？<br />\n港鐵之類？</blockquote><br />\n睇多次我果句, 買股票唔係買佢當前價值, 而係買佢既將來<br />\n你認為間公司前景冇問題就去馬, 如果認為買指數型ETF更好就買ETF<br />\n冇對錯之分"},{"pid":"5a14c9df1cc6287635a2bb8416a6e57a669ef2aa","tid":416222,"uid":131323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:45:22.000Z","msg":"供果陣唔計通脹既<br />\n十年前五千蚊點同而家五千蚊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072ebd181317bcdb6a8a1172bd7849189e294c7e","tid":416222,"uid":150653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>供果陣唔計通脹既<br />\n十年前五千蚊點同而家五千蚊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n供期好短，1年或兩年。最多三年。不過打算供完，再揀第二隻隻再供，唔會選3年。"},{"pid":"e93d6b997ba4b027edb4716779a80506270a9dae","tid":416222,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"樓同股票既波幅點比"},{"pid":"62a305492948762b2128bc1622e3874ad6c55826","tid":416222,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}